---
const stack = [
  "Vue 3", "React", "TypeScript", "Design tokens", "Figma Code Connect", "Variables API",
  "Storybook", "Playwright", "Vitest", "WCAG 2.1 AA", "Core Web Vitals", "GitHub Actions",
  "MCP servers",
];
---
<section id="credibility" class="chapter chapter--flow">
  <div class="chapter-inner">
    <p class="cred-statement" data-cred-statement aria-hidden="true">
      Eight years. A design system of <em>60+</em> components across <em>three</em> product teams.
      <em>Two</em> hackathon wins, both shipped to production. Performance and accessibility held to
      budget, every release.
    </p>
    <span class="sr-only">
      Eight years. A design system of 60+ components across three product teams. Two hackathon wins,
      both shipped to production. Performance and accessibility held to budget, every release.
    </span>
    <ul class="cred-stack" data-cred-stack>
      {stack.map((s) => <li class="cred-tag">{s}</li>)}
    </ul>
  </div>
</section>
